                  <interp inst="t18311020-189-crimeloc1007" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18311020-189-off1004 t18311020-189-crimeloc1007"></join>. On the afternoon of the 5th of October I was behind my counter; I heard a noise, got over the counter, and saw the prisoner running away - I missed a piece of printed cotton from the lobby of my shop - I saw the prisoner running, and something hanging between his legs; I followed him, and saw him drop it opposite Mr. Bradley's door; I followed, and was within one yard of him, when he was stopped; the cotton was picked up, and carried to Mr. Bradley's.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18311020-189-person1283">
